caption:
A new office.
A higher perspective.

@kalpesh.kinariwala unveils the new @pantheon_development office in Business Bay above the Dubai skyline with a view that reflects the vision.

The colors have washed off but the feeling haven’t 🌈

Presented by @pantheon_development and Co powered by @vinayfashion

DJ Line-up:
@dichetas | @djgautamdxb | @djsohaildubai | @yogmusiic |
@nutron_dxb | @djbuddhadubai | @nitesh.djj

#HOLIVERSE #HoliInDubai #DubaiHoli #holiparty2026

This unreleased and beautiful version of Shiv Kailashon ke vaasi 🔱 is all the therapy you need! 

@rishabsmusic thank you for bringing your magic ✨ to DXB! 🫶🙏 Listening to you LIVE was not on my cards so soon but it is all Mahadev’s blessings! Your concert came at the right time for me and healed 15k of us in a magical way! 

Har Har Mahadev! 🔱

They say music is the shorthand of emotion. In exactly one week, we’ll be speaking that language together with A. R. Rahman. 

The vibe in Abu Dhabi is already shifting—can you feel it?

